## Future Enhancements

Planned improvements to the data format:

- **Streaming Support**: For very large datasets
- **Incremental Exports**: Export only new data since last export
- **Deduplication**: Automatic deduplication of duplicate job records
- **Data Retention**: Automatic pruning of old data on export
- **Custom Schemas**: Support for user-defined data schemas
- **Alternative Formats**: Support for Parquet, Avro, and other formats
